                    <span>This Book covers too many topics unnecessarily, so when you really want to go a little deep into a specific field and make yourself clear, that will be not possible.<BR>This book is not really suitable for real multi-threaded programmer. <BR>New multi-threaded leaners maybe will found it useful for basic concepts.</span>
                  
